See Makefiles for build configuration.

PocketSphinxLauncher is the main program.

PSTrainer.sh must also have its dependencies satisfied.  See the script for details, they are a few programs mostly from sphinxtrain.

Requirements:
	Gtk+-3.0
	Alsa utilities (arecord and aplay)
	sphinxbase, pocketsphinx, and sphinxtrain

https://github.com/echoline/PocketSphinxLauncher
